div.div: Age 41, Oh Jung-Seok. A man who did all kinds of misdeeds and put his life on the line for the organisation to gain the highest position. But who knew the end of his life would be so miserable… Jung-Seok’s ‘virtuous living’ project starts now, one by one. (Source: Naver, translated)

The once up-and-coming monster hunter Suho has plateaued at B Class, dashing his hopes of ever avenging his parents' deaths. Enter the ghost of the Cheonma, former divine Murim master and Suho's direct ancestor! Fortunately for Suho, the disembodied Cheonma needs a body to hunt down his arch nemesis, the Blood Demon, and Suho is the perfect fit. Will Suho strike a deal with the Cheonma to escape his rut and gain the power to finally avenge his parents?
(Source: WEBTOONS)
